msgid "Bland-Altman Plots"
msgstr "Bland-Altman プロット"

msgid ""
"Bland-Altman plots of the mean vs. difference for each variable pair, with "
"mean difference and limits of agreement."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Scatter plot of mean vs. difference of the two measurements. The middle "
